These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-1::.
City: berlin, miami
1. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |    2    |
| City   | berlin | miami |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-2::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: train, boat
1. the person driving the boat is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |
| Transport   | train | boat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-3::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: marigold, azalea
1. the person who growsmarigold is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |   2   |
| Flower   | azalea | marigold |

 #################################

 
